                    "resourceUri": "ui://widget/flights.html"
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "name": "get_aircraft_track",
            "description": "Get the flight track (waypoints) for an aircraft. icao24 must be a 6-character lowercase hex string (e.g. '3c675a'). time is a Unix timestamp within the flight's time window to retrieve a specific historical track; pass 0 to retrieve the most recent track. Use the first_seen_ts from a departure or arrival result to get the track for that flight.",
